title: Real Apparel Co. logo Long Sleeve Tee | Minimal Vintage Script, White Tee
description:
A soft, vintage-feel long sleeve that settles into your rotation and keeps coming back. Crafted from a thicker, environmentally-conscious cotton, this classic-fit tee drapes with relaxed confidence and a lived-in look. The clean, understated front script and subtle construction details — tubular knit body, ribbed collar, and shoulder tape — create a piece that looks simple but lasts. Wear it on slow mornings, layered under a jacket for an evening walk, or when you want something honest and low-key for a casual meet-up.

Product features
- Thicker vintage-feel cotton for a soft, lived-in texture
- Tubular knit (no side seams) reduces waste and improves drape
- Ribbed knit collar and shoulder tape for shape retention and stability
- Medium-weight fabric (6.0 oz/yd²) with classic fit; sewn-in label
- Fiber blends vary by color; runs slightly smaller than usual

Care instructions
- Non-chlorine: bleach as needed
- Do not dryclean
- Machine wash: cold (max 30C or 90F)
- Tumble dry: medium heat
- Do not iron
